Author: cynclsk_ns
Text: i’m so burnt out man. i’m sick of school, activities, everything. interacting with people every day is exhausting and everyone, even my friends, stress me out. im a shitty person and everything that goes wrong is my fault. i just want to nap until i don’t physically and mentally feel like shit anymore.

Author: Brief_Somewhere
Text: Idk but I guess here goes. . .  I also only have one actual friend and I have begun to push her away. Shes literally one of the most important people to me and I've been so beat down by life this year that I lie and avoid her and we went from talking every day to once this month. I dont want to bother her with all these life issues is all cause its hella depressing.
